In experiment.ger is the word grammar that's currently used At the end of that
file is a bunch of declarations, the files corresponding to these symbols,
which are used in the grammar, are in this directory.  The file all.pho
contains all of the files concatenated and gives may give a rough idea how big
the casio files would have to be. This file contains 7841 lines of snippets
used in the grammar.

